{"tid":2155430,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"短篇漫畫《一千○一》","createTime":"2020-08-13T19:15:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T00:17:19.000Z","uid":246648,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"438a457dadb5beab8ea3754ee36b9bc04dbbd880","tid":2155430,"uid":246648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T19:15:26.000Z","msg":"我記得本腎兩年前周圍搵呢篇漫畫，不過一無所獲<br />\n<br />\n今日終於比我搵返，好深刻<br />\n<br />\n令我驚訝既係原來係香港人畫既，最初我睇果時係英文以為外國短篇<br />\n<br />\n唔怪之得搵唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港漫畫家馮展鵬 Fcp 於2013 年《熱血少年》刊登的短篇漫畫作品《一千○一》:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j4wQCyV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj4wQCyV.jpg&h=9fb23f20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kRtb6sg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkRtb6sg.jpg&h=a694b399&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gN9raTW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgN9raTW.jpg&h=9a736e66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w7f2tFC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw7f2tFC.jpg&h=e247e77e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jG9e4dX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjG9e4dX.jpg&h=85fd5aef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WmKyAkD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWmKyAkD.jpg&h=98a0afdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U9s8pdY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU9s8pdY.jpg&h=0a28b26f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cw6MVkE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCw6MVkE.jpg&h=4268fedd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CNpZvTZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3